          <div class="timeline-date">2020</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="timeline-title">Official Launch</h3>
            <p>True Brew Birdie Ltd is officially founded in Cyprus, with a remote team of marketing rebels spread across Europe and the US. The company's manifesto attracts attention from entrepreneurs tired of conventional marketing approaches.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">2021</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
