            <p>The company's client portfolio collectively crosses $10M in revenue generated through True Brew Birdie's marketing systems. The team expands to 15 full-time rebels.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">2023</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
